FBIS4-40852 "drsov119_m_94002" FBIS-SOV-94-119 Daily Report 21 Jun 1994 Tajikistan Russian Border Guard Helipad Attacked; Man Detained Russian Border Guard Helipad Attacked; Man Detained LD2106081394 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0755 GMT 21 Jun 94 LD2106081394 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Galina Gridneva] [Text] Dushanbe 21 June TASS -- A helipad, belonging to the Russian Frontier Guard Regiment deployed in Tajiksitan, came udner fire on Monday afternoon. According to military sources, the firing was carried out from the neighbouring "Russia" collective farm which borders the Dushanbe airport. One man, suspected of carrying out the terroristic act, was detained. An investigation is underway.
